The paper discusses the use of relay-assisted OFDM-IM for improving spectral and energy efficiency in 5G networks. This topic falls under the areas of information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), communication (cs.COMM), systems and control (cs.SY), and multimedia (cs.MM). However, since the focus is on wireless networks and communication technologies, cs.IT and cs.NI are the most likely sub-categories.
